EcoTrack run steps are documented in README.md.

Quick start:
1. Enable Firebase Email/Password Authentication and create a Firestore database.
2. Add Firebase web keys to frontend\.env and Firebase Admin service account to backend\serviceAccountKey.json.
3. Start backend: cd backend && python -m venv .venv && .venv\Scripts\activate && pip install -r requirements.txt && python app.py
4. Start frontend: cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev
5. Open http://localhost:5173 and register/login.
